Fischer Praises Panel Decision to Stay Within Budget Limits

-- B y   A l i s a   O d e n h e i m e r
-- 
2011-10-09T11:24:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-09/fischer-praises-panel-decision-to-stay-within-budget-limits.html
Bank of Israel Governor Stanley
Fischer told the Cabinet today that the decision by the
Trajtenberg committee to keep its recommendations within the
budget limits was “responsible” and that the country shouldn’t
embark on any “adventures” at this time. Fischer’s remarks
were released in a text message.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alisa Odenheimer in Jerusalem at 
 aodenheimer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
